<template>
  <section id="step-for">
    <input-form
      v-if="arrayInputs"
      :propArrayInputs="arrayInputs"
      v-on:validateInputs="validateInputs"
    />
  </section>
</template>

<script lang="ts">
  import { Component, Prop, Vue } from "vue-property-decorator";
  import { cpf as CPF } from "cpf-cnpj-validator";

  import { InputForms, TypeHelp } from "@/models/inputForms";
  @Component({})
  export class StepFour extends Vue {
    @Prop() propArrayInputs!: InputForms[];

    public arrayInputs: InputForms[] = this.propArrayInputs;
    public step = "stepFour";

    mounted() {
      this.setNextDisabled();
    }

    public validateInputs(inputs: InputForms[]) {
      const stepModel: Array<{}> = [];

      this.setNextDisabled();

      if (inputs[2].showInput) {
        if (inputs[2] && inputs[2].model) {
          if (this.validateCPF(inputs[2].model)) {
            this.setHelp(inputs, 2, "Este CPF é valido", "valid");
            this.$emit("setNextDisabled", true);
            inputs[2].model = this.formatCPF(inputs[2].model);
          } else {
            this.setHelp(inputs, 2, "Este CPF é invalido", "invalid");
            this.$emit("setNextDisabled", false);
          }
        }
      }

      inputs.forEach((input) => {
        stepModel.push(input.model);
        this.storageInputsStep(stepModel);
      });
    }

    private setNextDisabled() {
      this.arrayInputs[0].model && this.arrayInputs[1].model
        ? this.$emit("setNextDisabled", true)
        : this.$emit("setNextDisabled", false);

      if (this.arrayInputs[2].showInput) {
        this.arrayInputs[2].model && this.arrayInputs[2].model
          ? this.$emit("setNextDisabled", true)
          : this.$emit("setNextDisabled", false);
      }
    }

    private setHelp(
      inputs: InputForms[],
      index: number,
      helpMsg: string,
      type: TypeHelp
    ) {
      switch (type) {
        case "valid":
          this.setClassAndHelp(inputs, index, "help", helpMsg);
          this.setClassAndHelp(
            inputs,
            index,
            "classHelp",
            "form-text valid-feedback"
          );
          this.setClassAndHelp(
            inputs,
            index,
            "classInput",
            "form-control is-valid"
          );
          break;
        case "invalid":
          this.setClassAndHelp(inputs, index, "help", helpMsg);
          this.setClassAndHelp(
            inputs,
            index,
            "classHelp",
            "form-text invalid-feedback"
          );
          this.setClassAndHelp(
            inputs,
            index,
            "classInput",
            "form-control is-invalid"
          );
          break;
        case "normal":
          this.setClassAndHelp(inputs, index, "help", helpMsg);
          this.setClassAndHelp(
            inputs,
            index,
            "classHelp",
            "form-text text-muted"
          );
          this.setClassAndHelp(inputs, index, "classInput", "form-control");
          break;
      }
    }

    private setClassAndHelp(
      inputs: InputForms[],
      index: number,
      name: string,
      value: string
    ) {
      inputs[index][name] = value;
    }

    private validateCPF(cpf: string): boolean {
      return CPF.isValid(cpf);
    }

    private formatCPF(cpf: string): string {
      return CPF.format(cpf);
    }

    private storageInputsStep(inputsModel: Array<{}>) {
      this.$emit("storageInputsStep", this.step, inputsModel);
    }
  }

  export { StepFour as default };
</script>

<style lang="scss" scoped></style>
